## Regional Analysis
Throughout the projected time, Europe is anticipated to rule the world market. In terms of revenue share in 2023, Europe came in first with 38.2%. Due in large part to strict energy efficiency rules and a strong emphasis on sustainability, the region is leading the way in the adoption of smart lighting solutions.

